All Implemented Interfaces:
org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, ICUCorrectionProposal, ICommandAccess, IJavaCompletionProposal, org.eclipse.jface.text.contentassist.ICompletionProposal, org.eclipse.jface.text.contentassist.ICompletionProposalExtension5, org.eclipse.jface.text.contentassist.ICompletionProposalExtension6
public class ASTRewriteCorrectionProposal extends CUCorrectionProposal
A proposal for quick fixes and quick assists that works on an AST rewrite. Either a rewrite is directly passed in the constructor or the method getRewrite() is overridden to provide the AST rewrite that is evaluated on the document when the proposal is applied.
Since:
3.8
